fireclient.module.generic.visibility_tog: Sets whether this module is visible
fireclient.module.armor_display.lock_but: Sets whether the position is locked to the hotbar
fireclient.module.generic.enabled_toggle: Sets whether this module is enabled
fireclient.module.coordinates.other_dime: Sets whether the other dimension (Overworld/Nether)'s scaled coordinates are shown
fireclient.module.coordinates.window_mod: Shows a separate window for coordinates. Useful for streaming/screenshares!
fireclient.module.nametag.darker_backgro: Toggles whether the nametag has a darker background, making it easier to see
fireclient.module.nametag.show_own: Toggles whether you can see your own nametag
